OL,6,FA motorcyclist who died in a crash has
OL,7,Fbeen described as a 'devoted husband
OL,8,Fand father'.
OL,10,F62-year-old Rob Love from Wiltshire
OL,11,Fdied on the A350 West Ashton when his
OL,12,FYamaha YP 400 collided with a
OL,13,FVolkswagen Taigo.
OL,15,FThe crash happened on 17 December at
OL,16,Faround 9.10pm. Mr Love's family has
OL,17,Fpaid tribute to him.
OL,19,FThe statement said: "Rob was a devoted
OL,20,Fhusband, father and grampy/grampsie to
OL,21,Fhis three grandchildren.
