OL,3,CMotorcyclist who died in crash was a
OL,4,C'devoted husband and father'
OL,6,F"Born to military parents in England
OL,7,Fbut raised in Edinburgh with his
OL,8,Fsister Marnie, Rob joined the Royal
OL,9,FScots Dragoon Guards in 1980 and
OL,10,Fserved as a gunner mech for 13 years
OL,11,Fwhich included active service during
OL,12,Fthe Gulf War in 1990.
OL,14,F"Rob was based in Warminster where he
OL,15,Fmet his wife, Sue, in 1987 and they
OL,16,Fmarried the following year. They
OL,17,Fenjoyed 37 years together with their
OL,18,Fson Stuart and stepchildren Antony and
OL,19,FRichard.
