OL,3,CMotorcyclist who died in crash was a
OL,4,C'devoted husband and father'
OL,6,F"They settled in Westbury and resided
OL,7,Fthere for over 30 years where Rob
OL,8,Fenjoyed many hobbies particularly
OL,9,Fwalking his dogs Sam, Bruce and Ralphy
OL,10,Fand spending time socialising with his
OL,11,Fneighbours who he had become closer to
OL,12,Fduring the pandemic with the
OL,13,Faffectionately named 'Back Lane Gang'.
OL,15,F"He was also a passionate scooter
OL,16,Frider who enjoyed organised events
OL,17,Fwith the local biking community (the
OL,18,FMaxi Muppets).
